Subject: Enter: The Jaguar
From: "Tara M" <jagris@...>

No one was around when she awoke. Looking up at the inside of her stasis pod while listening to the computer outside program her with a beast mode, her memories started coming back... Cybertron, a group of people she knew, a chip. She couldn't have the computer give her a beast mode... no. There was a reason. Activating an internal command, she overrode the computer's systems, downloading the jaguar DNA in the protocol chip she carried.

*Much better. Now... how do I get the slag outta this titanium pea pod?*

Opening a comlink on any and all frequencies, she calmly started. "This is Jagris. Is anyone within my vicinity? I need assistance."
